            <Title>Willa Cather article for comparison</Title>
            <Text>We believe that the benefits of the work we have performed on Cather’s personal voice are not limited to Cather studies. The potential applications of this type of statistical analysis in literature studies as a whole are wide reaching. Many authors have left behind extensive collections of personal writing that could hold untapped insight into how they communicated in different settings, and how their writing evolved.</Text>
